Author: FastInvest
Title: Online Investment Bank.
Body: During the ICO  crowdsale, 20% of Marketing budget will be constituted to FIT token holders as an Affiliate Commission. The affiliate commission will be distributed every week in Ethereum cryptocurrency. For example,  if our Marketing budget is 7,500,000 $, proportionally 1,500,000 $ will be devoted to the affiliate commission. This means, that if a holder has 1% of all outstanding Fast Invest tokens, he will receive 1% of all Affiliate Commission share that will be spent every week.

Author: jhenfelipe
Title: Online Investment Bank.
Body: There will be a 2nd phase of ICO, if when exactly there's no announcement yet. Anyone could register in their whitelist to receive timely updates about it. As mentioned in their telegram, they will be changing the ICO price and those who bought in the first phase could exchange their tokens with the new price to get more token.  @Angelo Santos is right. The team is active in telegram, so for questions or any concerns it would be better to ask there because they are not active here in the forum.   EDIT: Just to add (don't want to make another post for this). Posted by: Dovile | FAST INVEST via telegram Quote Dear community member and FIT token holders,  Let us shortly introduce our finalized further actions and strategy that takes FIT tokens.  Firstly, we continue Fast Invest Token crowdsale. The brand new FIT will be based on USD price, not an Ethereum. It means that the rapidly changing Ethereum price will not affect the FIT token price. The new FIT token price will start from 0,01 USD. The detailed pricing we will announce until 01/04/2018.  As the token price changes, the supply of new  FIT token will be 2bn entirely.  Besides, we are extending our ICO timing. The current crowdsale will end on 01/04/2019, or it will last until all tokens are sold.  We emphasize that current FIT token holders will be able to exchange it for new FIT tokens on new price range. At the moment we are creating a tool on our website that will automatically transfer current FIT tokens, to new ones. What is noble, that everyone who will make this conversion, will get 10% bonus.  We will enable this tool on the 1st of April or even earlier. Follow our announcements.  Shortly updating that we are developing our investment platform and following the planned roadmap. At the moment, we are finalizing mobile app, and we have already created an enterprise in the USA, also started prototyping premium crypto-account.  Only with the community help, we can build an extraordinary investment platform and merge two worlds - fiat and crypto. Your support is exceptionally very important to us.  Thank you very much for your backing.

Author: masimc2
Title: Online Investment Bank.
Body: What gives this coin value?  As far as I can tell the company is already established and profitable. By owning the coin you do not own the company or have a share in any of its profits. The only benefit I can see from ownership of this coin (and minimum 1000 coins at that) is full access to their platform. What does full access give me? The ability to transfer crypto for fiat (and possibly earn interest on crypto??). At what rates will crypto be exchanged for fiat? I do not know. Can I withdraw the fiat? I assume so but I am not sure. To withdraw the fiat from crypto account, the verification requirements of the country you are a citizen of come into play.  So basically, big picture as I see it, I cannot see what gives this coin value (ie. why would people be wanting to buy it off me and why wouldn't I want to sell it).  Can someone please elaborate on these thoughts??  Thankyou,  masimc2.

Title: Online Investment Bank.

Author: FastInvest
Title: Online Investment Bank.
Body: The main and the most important difference is that we are not a start up, we are real FinTech business. Here are some proof: - since 2015 we have been developing investment to consumer loans platform and today we have final version (not beta version); - we have more than 8000 customers across the Europe, that use our financial tools daily; - our business was not funded any angel funds, we build Fast Invest from our own funds; - we have necessary licences and permissions for our business; - we are developing financial tools that would be easy to understand. Our aim is that everyone can be an investors, so we build user-friendly platform.

Author: FastInvest
Title: Online Investment Bank.
Body: Thank you for the question. To start with, I should mention that FAST INVEST is already operating business, having working investment platform (not a prototype) many customers across the Europe and globally, professional and enthusiastic team. However, we are expanding our platform and building new infrastructure on the blockchain to offer new digital banking products, mostly related with investing. Our value comes from merging fiat and cryptocurrencies. FAST INVEST community members will have a possibility to use both types of currencies for their daily banking operations. Service like Crypto-proved lending allows users to get a loan in fiat currency and keep the value of bitcoins or ethereums. Digital wallet and digital currency exchange, payment card will enable customer use both types of currencies.  We’ve set ourselves the goal of positively impacting the lives of millions of people using the latest technologies.
